/// <reference no-default-lib="true"/>

interface ObjectConstructor {
    /**
     * Determines whether an object has a property with the specified name.
     * @param o An object.
     * @param v A property name.
     */
    hasOwn(o: object, v: PropertyKey): boolean;
}
